    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超越普通的爱情故事，体验 <strong>&quot;Date or Destiny: Kiss or Miss.&quot;</strong> 控制被父亲赶出家的年轻人 Kaan，随波逐流、迷失人生。在充满陌生人和惊喜的城市里，由你来决定他的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127030/extras/46da6f539508a527c989a6538eea58fd.avif?t=1751035600\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127030/extras_big/46da6f539508a527c989a6538eea58fd.avif?t=1751035600 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认识新朋友。谨慎选择你的话语。决定信任谁，远离谁，跟随你的心还是理智。每个选择都会带来不同的后果，每个瞬间都是转折点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127030/extras/cd23dbf11f1d78b6b94a9739d0689a08.avif?t=1751035600\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127030/extras_big/cd23dbf11f1d78b6b94a9739d0689a08.avif?t=1751035600 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坠入爱河，面对心碎，揭开秘密。敢于冒险，大胆行动，引导 Kaan 开启一段可能以激情、悔恨或意外结局收尾的旅程。</p>",
